The paper deals with image denoising, which is a common problem in computer vision and image processing. Therefore, cs.CV (Computer Vision and Pattern Recognition) is the most likely sub-category. The proposed method involves the use of TSPs and optimization techniques, which are common in machine learning and artificial intelligence, making cs.AI the second likely sub-category. The paper also discusses the computational aspects of the method, which could fall under cs.LG (Machine Learning) or cs.IT (Information Theory).
